{
    "code": "MQ_CHURN_SUB_PER_MONTH",
    "description": "Subscription Churn per month",
    "disabled": false,
    "dimension1": "subscriptions",
    "dimension2": "terminations",
    "dimension3": "",
    "dimension4": "",
    "editable": false,
    "additive": false,
    "sqlQuery": "
with  
subscriptions as (
select 
count(s.id) as count
from billing_subscription s
where 
date_trunc('month', s.subscription_date) = date_trunc('month', to_date('#{date}','YYYY-MM-DD'))
),
terminations as (
select 
count(s.id) as count
from billing_subscription s
where 
date_trunc('month', s.termination_date) = date_trunc('month', to_date('#{date}','YYYY-MM-DD'))
)
select
s.count-t.count as trend,
s.count as subscriptions,
t.count as terminations
from subscriptions s, terminations t
		  ",
    "measurementPeriod": "MONTHLY",
    "lastMeasureDate":""
}

{
    "code": "MQ_ORDERS_BY_STATUS",
    "description": "Order by status",
    "disabled": false,
    "dimension1": "pending",
    "dimension2": "validated",
    "dimension3": "cancelled",
    "dimension4": "null",
    "editable": false,
    "additive": false,
    "sqlQuery": "
with
       value as (select count(o.id) from ord_order o where status in ('IN_CREATION')),
       pending as (select count(o.id) from ord_order o where status in ('ACKNOWLEDGED','IN_PROGRESS','PENDING','PARTIAL','HELD')),
       validated as (select count(o.id) from ord_order o where status in ('COMPLETED')),
       cancelled as (select count(o.id) from ord_order o where status in ('REJECTED','FAILED','CANCELLED'))
select
        value.count as value,
        pending.count as pending,
        validated.count as validated,
        cancelled.count as cancelled
from
        value,
        pending,
        validated,
        cancelled
;
            ",
    "measurementPeriod": "DAILY",
    "lastMeasureDate":"2017-12-01"
}

{
    "code": "MQ_MRR_REC_PER_MONTH_PER_OFFER",
    "description": "MRR per offer (recurring Wallet Operations per month)",
    "disabled": false,
    "dimension1": "offer1",
    "dimension2": "offer2",
    "dimension3": "offer3",
    "dimension4": "offer4",
    "editable": false,
    "additive": false,
    "sqlQuery": "
with
mrr as
(
   select
       wo.offer_code,
       round(sum(wo.amount_without_tax),2) as value
   from
       billing_wallet_operation wo
   where
       wo.end_date is not null
   and date_trunc('month', wo.operation_date) = date_trunc('month', to_date('#{date}','YYYY-MM-DD'))
   group by
       wo.offer_code, date_trunc('month', wo.operation_date)
)
select
   coalesce((select sum(value) from mrr where offer_code not in ('OF_CLASSIC_MAIN','OF_CLASSIC_REC','OF_CLASSIC_TEMPLATE','OF_FUTURE_01')),0) as others,
   coalesce((select sum(value) from mrr where offer_code='OF_CLASSIC_MAIN'),0) as offer1,
   coalesce((select sum(value) from mrr where offer_code='OF_CLASSIC_REC'),0) as offer2,
   coalesce((select sum(value) from mrr where offer_code='OF_CLASSIC_TEMPLATE'),0) as offer3,
   coalesce((select sum(value) from mrr where offer_code='OF_FUTURE_01'),0) as offer4
        ",
    "measurementPeriod": "MONTHLY",
    "lastMeasureDate":"2017-01-01"
}

{  "code": "MQ_MRR_REC_PER_MONTH_SUBS1",
        "description": "MRR per Subscription Status (recurring Wallet Operations per month)",
        "disabled": false,
        "dimension1": "regular",
        "dimension2": "new",
        "dimension3": "upsell",
        "dimension4": "cancelled",
        "editable": false,
        "additive": false,
        "sqlQuery": "
select 
    currmonth.regular + currmonth.new + currmonth.upsell + currmonth.cancelled as curr_total,
    currmonth.regular as curr_regular,
    currmonth.new as curr_new,
    currmonth.upsell as curr_upsell,
    currmonth.cancelled as curr_cancelled

from
(
with a as
(
    SELECT round(sum(wo.amount_without_tax),2) as value ,
    date_trunc('month', coalesce(ua.subscription_date, date '2000-01-01')) as ua_creation_month,
		   date_trunc('month', coalesce(s.subscription_date, date '2000-01-01')) as su_subscription_month,
		   date_trunc('month', coalesce(s.termination_date, date '3000-01-01')) as su_termination_month,
		   date_trunc('month', coalesce(wo.operation_date, date '2000-01-01')) as wo_operation_month
    FROM
        billing_wallet_operation wo
        inner join billing_charge_instance ci on ci.id = wo.charge_instance_id
        inner join cat_recurring_charge_templ rc on rc.id = ci.charge_template_id
        inner join billing_subscription s on s.id = ci.subscription_id
        inner join billing_user_account ua on ua.id = s.user_account_id

    WHERE 
    	date_trunc('month', wo.operation_date)=date_trunc('month', to_date('#{date}','YYYY-MM-DD') - interval '1 month')
		AND wo.end_date is not null
	and wo.operation_type='W'
    GROUP BY
     ua_creation_month,
	   su_subscription_month,
	   su_termination_month,
	   wo_operation_month
    )
select
    coalesce((select sum(a.value) from a),0) as total,
    coalesce((select sum(a.value) from a where (a.su_subscription_month != a.wo_operation_month) and (a.su_termination_month >= a.wo_operation_month) ),0) as regular,
